title: Illegal Serves
description:
Smudged eyeliner, illegal serves and husbands are once again lurking, but that doesn’t stop Jessica and June from rejecting the “back to school” rush. Then, the gals chat sleepovers and summer camp. Jessica is still planning on a Pickleball summer and regales us with tales of her Hugh Grant haircut. Then, June and Jessica announce the winners of the In Pickleball Magazine giveaway. Remember Deep Divers, this is (un)fortunately a Pickleball podcast now.
